dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for St. Croix County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, St_Croix_Addresses_2014.gdb. [Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Site Address Points]
